- shortcut(eclipse keymap)

	- default
		- nav
			- source기준 navi: A-f1

		- code assist: A-enter

		- pannel
			- pannel toggle: A-{1~9}

		- windows
			- close: C-f4 / C-S-f4 << custom todo
			- split: C-S-A split
			  switcher: C-TAB
			- focus to source: ESC or F12
			- full source screen..?: S-F12

			- bookmark source: C-S-{1~9}
			  goto marking: C-{1~9}

		- search
			- all: S-S
			- actions: C-S-a
			- file search all: C-S-r
			- recent
				- location: C-S-e
				- file recent: C-e
			- find in path: C-h
			- impl: C-t
			- find useage: C-g

		- multiple cursor
			- 단어선택: A-y / A-C-Y
			- todo 멀티커서 생성??

		- run/debug
			- debug 실행했던것: A-S-d

		- error message view TODO
			- previous hightlighted error: S-f1
			  라인에 커서 올려놓으면 좌하단에 메시지나옴

			- C-f1
			  퀵픽스...

	- custom
		- Clone Caret Above: C-A-Up
		- Clone Caret Below: C-A-Down
		- Duplicate Entire Lines: A-S-Down


